headline: Is It Time To Reassess IQVIA (IQV) After A 22% One Year Share Price Gain
summary: If you are wondering whether IQVIA Holdings is fairly priced or if there is still room for value, this article walks you through what the current share price might be implying. The stock last closed at US$241.57, with returns of 0.4% over 7 days, 8.7% over 30 days, 7.2% year to date and 22.0% over the past year, which may have shifted how the market sees its risk and opportunity. Recent attention on IQVIA has centered on its role as a large player in contract research and real world data...
